rows.label: qev015703_MSG0001
rows.name: You find that stinking whimsical duoguill?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015703_MSG0002
rows.name:
If you can't even find it when you're trying to,
I'm REALLY jealous of your luck.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015703_MSG0003
rows.name:
If you trace the route back, you're almost guaranteed
to run across the thing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015703_MSG0004
rows.name: Go find the big lug and sock it one for me, yeah?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015703_MSG0005
rows.name:
Well? You beat that whimsical duoguill
into next week yet?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015703_MSG0006
rows.name:
Hold on, now. Judging from the air of confidence
and the smug grin on your face...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015703_MSG0007
rows.name: I'd say that baby's six feet under![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015703_MSG0008
rows.name: Well, shoot. That's music to my ears.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015703_MSG0009
rows.name:
You cleared the path and made my day to boot!
Pretty impressive stuff.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015703_MSG0010
rows.name: I really gotta thank you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015703_MSG0011
rows.name:
Well, while you were off fighting, I was working on
this Skell. Almost got it all patched up.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015703_MSG0012
rows.name:
Looks like we'll be getting back to work without losing
much time, thanks to you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015703_MSG0013
rows.name:
We'll bang these data probes in at the FrontierNav
probe sites and be back home in time for supper.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015703_MSG0014
rows.name:
Hopefully the indigen data they churn out will make
sure no one else gets another nasty surprise.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015703_JNK0010
rows.name: Support[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015703_SEL0011
rows.name: Give Myles's plan the thumbs-up.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015703_JNK0020
rows.name: Inquire[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015703_SEL0021
rows.name:
Ask Myles where the FrontierNav
probe placement sites are.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015703_MSG0015
rows.name: Hey, thanks![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015703_MSG0016
rows.name:
The Pathfinders are an elite group even by BLADE
standards, which means average schlubs like me
have gotta work extra hard to keep up.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015703_MSG0017
rows.name:
And THAT means it's time for me to patch this Skell up
and get back to work.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015703_MSG0018
rows.name:
One's just a ways northwest of here,
on the shore of a lake.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015703_MSG0019
rows.name: The other one's in a cave to the northeast.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015703_MSG0020
rows.name:
I was thinking my team could snatch 'em both up
before all this happened.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015703_MSG0021
rows.name:
If you're headed that way, they're all yours.
Just be careful.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015703_MSG0022
rows.name: Some planet we picked to crash into, huh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015703_MSG0023
rows.name:
Heh. It's easy to forget how nuts this place is until you
get your ass handed to you by some giant monster.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015703_MSG0024
rows.name:
I mean, for the foreseeable future, we're probably
gonna be fighting things that can easily crush Skells.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015703_MSG0025
rows.name:
I gotta remember to be a lot more careful,
or I'm gonna wind up a lot more dead.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015703_MSG0026
rows.name: No more rookie mistakes for me from here on out![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015703_MSG0027
rows.name:
You be careful too, yeah? Let's the both of us live a
long, long time. See where humanity goes, you know?[ST:wait ]
